values: I'm SO EXCITED! It's only 3 more days until my best friends BIG DAY! She's so excited but stressed along with it! I've decided to sing a song at their wedding! Martina McBride's "There You Are"! It's so pretty and Martina is her favourite artist so it works! Yep so instead of doing a speech which by the way may I add I'm horrible at doing, I've decided to sing my words to her and Kevin! Should be a beautiful wedding! Well I've been training at Teletech for about 2 weeks now! Not so bad so far! I give them a lot more credit then what most people have said about the company! Man getting up everyday for 6 has been friggin hard! I'M SO TIRED! Pat and I go to bed like at 10! Which never used to happen as Cyn might know! We're like night owls! Especially her! And well she kept me awake sometimes! OH NO WAIT THAT WAS MARTIN'S FAULT! STUPID MARTIN! Oh man I miss my S4 people! I miss being on my own! I MISS MY ROOMATE AND HER SILLY WAYS! OH CYNTHIA you superstitious girl you! Gotta jet!

I've just realized that no one leaves me comments on this thing! How sad is that! So basically I'm writing this journal for nothing! Yep! Don't see the point anymore until people start leaving me comments!

SO yeah! It's almost the end of this long weekend and it has SUCKED SO FAR! I've done nothing really! The only great thing is that I got my hair trial done for the wedding! It's really nice and it suits the shape of my face! I can't wait for the wedding now! Only 4 more weeks! Oh Elaina and I put together the slide show of her and Kevin! She put in the pictures of Kevin kissing me and Pat kissing her! HAHAHA... and it goes perfectly with the song that will be in the background! Oh man! I finally started tanning today! I think I burnt a little but that's ok! First time I always burn! I think I'll go Tuesday and then Thursday and then I have to start using my Mom's sessions because I have no more left and I can't afford it right now! So finally my freckles have come out! HEHEHE... We had a birthday celebration for my friend JF on Friday! I thought the guy hated me after the incident with the girls and the bar at the beginning of the month but actually he was wondering where I had been! He missed me! AWWWW... I love Jf... So yeah! ANyways I have to jet!! Going to bed soon! Cynthia!! COMMENT MY JOURNAL! HAHAHA.... you're the only one who reads the damn things anyways!

Ok I know I haven't been writing in this thing in a while but I've been VERY VERY BUSY!!! I've been home for almost a month now and everything is about my best friends Wedding! We've been busy with the stag and doe and her surprise bridal shower and now it's only 4 weeks away! AHHH how nuts is that? Man I'm going to cry SO MUCH at this thing I don't know what I'm going to do with myself! So yeah I have no job! I'm so poor I don't know what to do! It's May Long weekend and I HAVE NOTHING TO DO!! AHHH I'm so pissed off! I just want a call back already. I'm tired of this waiting around shit! Just someone hire me! I should have enough qualifications! COME ON!!! Something should come up soon otherwise I'm SCREWED with no money and nothing to do all summer! Ok enough of that! I would like to take this time to say HAPPY BIRTHDAY TO MY Girl and ROOMIE CYNTHIA!!! Have a good one girl! You deserve everything you've ever wanted! Wish I could be there!! xoxoxoxo

Life is lived forwards but understood backwards

So that was the quote that my Psych Prof gave us in lecture yesturday! It actually makes sense though! You live your life forward but to fully understand it you have to go back to the past! AH HA... BRILLIANT! Yes I know I'm a geek but seriously I find the stuff really interesting! Hmmm... maybe I should read some of it then! Stupid Megan...

So I've decided that we should go to a pub for my birthday! I think I will have more fun and I think everyone else will have more fun! If the pub gets boring we can always head over to Louie's or something! Yes... 4 more days! Yippee! I'm actually being sarcastic there! Who the hell wants to be 20 honestly? What good does it do? You're no longer considered a teenager and can't get away with the things you used to do. Older adults now feel that you're an adult and should take more responsibility and stuff! MAN! THIS SUCKS! Well, it's not all that bad but it has it's down falls.

SO Cynthia watched a few episodes of OC without me today! HOW RUDE? We are OC buddies! We started watching them together we should finish watching them together! GRRRR.... She said she'd watch them again but it's not the same! She'll already know what happens!!

Pat got food poisoning the other day! Poor boy! He was so sick and didn't even tell me till like 10:00 at night when he had the chance all day to tell me. Then I asked him if he wanted me to call my Mom to get him something to help the pain he said "Well I don't want to bother her" I'm like you're not the one going to be bothering her I AM... So I called anyway after his rejection! HAHAHA... I WIN! FINALLY...

I think a shower sounds good right about now! I can go bug Cynthia too! She'll probably kill me! HAHAHAHA... bye bye...

So yeah! I'm almost 20! AHHH... I don't know if I want to be 20! Because people keep freaking me out by saying stuff like "Hey think about it in 10 years you'll be 30!" 30! FUCK! I'm not thinking of 30! I'm not even done school yet!! I mean it's a good thing and it's a bad thing! No longer can I be called a teenager and I have to act like an adult now! But then I guess it's a cool thing because I'm an adult and finally get people to take me seriously!

So I'm thinking I want to go out to a pub for my birthday! Everyone keeps telling me different things. Lets go to Louie's, let's go to a pub! I DON'T CARE... as long as I'm having a good time it doesn't matter to me where we go! I'm hoping people come out! That would be really nice! I already know of a few people but every birthday always turns into a disaster someway somehow! Lets make this the year that it won't be destroyed or ruined!

Anyways, I think it's time for me to do some productive work now! BYE BYE!

I'm DONE MIDTERMS! Yeah! It was really nice to just relax today and not have to rush and do a bunch of work at once! Just took my time today and RELAXED! Always nice to relax once in a while when University can be so hectic! So I watched a really good movie with Sarah today. It was called Under the Tuscan Sun! A REALLY GOOD MOVIE! I swear if anyone ever does that to me I'm moving to Tuscany and buying that damn house!! SO THAT I CAN EXPERIENCE THAT STUFF!! Oh wait I forgot it's a DAMN MOVIE! Nothing ever happens like that in real life! For all I know I could end up losing all my money there and have to get on the plane back to CANADA! Anyways, I think the roomie is home! Gotta jet!!

So I'm having a great day so far! Nothing really exciting but nothing really bad either! SUCH A BEAUTIFUL DAY!!! The sun is shining and the SNOW IS MELTING! YIPPEE!!!! The only thing is I have a midterm on Thursday that I have to do well on! STUPID MIDTERMS... But at least I'm done Thursday! YEAH!!

So nothing else is really new! Oh, this Thursday we're all heading out to Patty McFlarety's for Eric's 20th Birthday! SHOULD BE FUN!! I'm turning 20 in 19 days! YIPPEE! HAPPY BIRTHDAY TO ME! I'm going to be SO OLD!! I guess that's how life goes!

Anyways, enough procrastinating I have to do some more studying! Somone send me a comment god damnit!! I've got no comments! BOO HOO :'(

So yeah, I had the best weekend ever!! Pat, my Dad and Rosa all came up on Thursday night and stayed until today! It was really awesome... So then on Friday after I was done classes we all went up to London to meet Pat's other side of the family! WOW... was I nervous!! His sister and brother are so nice and we're planning a trip of some sort for them to come visit or we go down! Whatever works best! Him and his sister look so much alike! Pat has to send me pictures! Then after coming back from London, Pat and I went to Mongolian for some martinis and to just sit back and talk and what not! Saturday morning we headed to T-Dot! That was fun too! We did some shopping and swimming! Went out for beer and pizza that night! Then went swimming some more! STUPID BITCH AT THE SWIMMING POOL THOUGH! Have a staring problem much? There was this woman as soon as we entered the pool who just kept staring at us and giving us nasty looks! I seriously have no clue what her problem was! Then there was these two little old ladies who did the same thing!! PEOPLE THESE DAYS! Can't people just mind their own business! Then we headed back to Waterloo today and had some food at Kelsey's! I wish they had stayed the extra day! OH WELL! Can't win them all! Awesome weekend, now I'm back to reality of studying for my midterm this Thursday! LAST ONE! WHOO HOO! Thank god!

SO yeah I've been studying all friggin day for this stupid midterm and I really don't feel like it anymore! I think I'm pretty much ready for it! You never know though!! I may get my ass kicked by it! That's why I'm going to continue to study until 6:00... right now I'm just taking a break! NEED ONE FOR SURE! Trying to help Cynthia decide on what to wear this weekend for her parties in good ol T-DOT! She's one complicated girl!! Seriously, our tastes are not the same at all! But you know what they say "Opposites Attract"! HAHAHA... Anyways, back to the drawing board!

So I was having the worst day ever yesturday! Boo URNS! Anyways, I had a Psych midterm yesturday I didn't feel ready for and I also did horrible on my Chem Midterm! CHEM SUCKS ASS! If Chem were a woman I'd call her a whore and kick her ass! I get home from my midterm yesturday and I get this email from my Dad saying he's bringing Pat and Rosa down with him tomorrow! YIPPEE! I'm so EXCITED! So they're all staying down in Waterloo till Monday! A weekend with my hunnie! ROCK ON! So yeah I have a midterm tomorrow night but I'm not worried about it because it's CS (stupid CS) and it's super easy! Well, maybe I'm a little too confident about it! I'm still going to need to study for it! Anyways, food is calling me and so is reading my lab for tonight! NIGHT LABS SUCK ASS!!
